    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## ⚙️ Before You Start\n\nBefore enabling this workflow:\n\n1. Replace **all placeholders** in every HTTP node\n2. Configure **Proxmox credentials** (HTTP Header Auth)\n3. Configure **BookStack credentials** (HTTP Header Auth)\n4. Enable **QEMU Guest Agent** on all QEMU VMs\n5. Run manually **once** before enabling the schedule\n\nSee `docs/installation.md` for step-by-step instructions.",
        "height": 280,
        "width": 420,
        "color": 7
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -2200,
