      ],
      "id": "sticky-intro-001",
      "name": "📋 Setup Instructions"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 🔐 Proxmox API Token\n\nThis workflow uses the **Proxmox REST API**.\n\nCreate a dedicated **read-only** API token:\n\n```\nPVEAPITOKEN=user@realm!tokenid=secret\n```\n\nMinimum required permissions:\n- `VM.Audit`\n- `Sys.Audit`\n- `Datastore.Audit`\n\nSee `docs/proxmox-api-token.md`",
        "height": 260,
        "width": 380,
        "color": 3
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -1700,
        -380
      ],
      "id": "sticky-proxmox-001",
      "name": "🔐 Proxmox API Note"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 🖥️ QEMU Guest Agent\n\nQEMU IP discovery requires the **QEMU Guest Agent** to be installed and running inside each VM.\n\nIf no IP is returned for a VM:\n1. Check the agent is installed: `qemu-guest-agent`\n2. Check it is enabled in Proxmox VM options\n3. Check it is running: `systemctl status qemu-guest-agent`\n\nSee `docs/troubleshooting.md`",
        "height": 240,
        "width": 380,
        "color": 4
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -1100,
        640
      ],
      "id": "sticky-qemu-001",
      "name": "🖥️ QEMU Agent Note"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 📚 BookStack Integration\n\nBookStack pages are updated via the **BookStack API**.\n\n- Use **dedicated pages** for generated inventory\n- Never point to a page with manual documentation\n- Retrieve the Page ID from the BookStack URL\n\nSee `docs/bookstack-setup.md`",
        "height": 220,
        "width": 360,
        "color": 5
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        900,
        -320
      ],
      "id": "sticky-bookstack-001",
      "name": "📚 BookStack Note"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 🔔 ntfy Notifications\n\n`ntfy` is **optional** — used only for workflow error notifications.\n\nIf you don't use ntfy:\n- Delete or disable `Error Trigger` and `Send ntfy Error Notification`\n- No other part of the workflow is affected\n\nSelf-hosted ntfy: https://ntfy.sh/docs/install/",
        "height": 200,
        "width": 340,
        "color": 6
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
